&lt;P&gt;It does make sense that there are some beings that are immune to tracking, but they should be sparse and only exist with good reason. After all, as rogues, we are arguing that fewer creatures should see through our stealth... isn't that the same kind of problem? A class ability that we need to be reliable to be able to, well, rely on it?&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;I realize there is not a lot of love lost between ranjahs and us rogues, but this one we should be on the same side of. To be otherwise would be hypocritical.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
