ight lamp should reveal me. I think rangers should only be able to track trackable mobs. Yes, it is a fantasy game, but where is this rule that fantasy should be completely unbelievable. The best fantasy always allows for the suspension of disbelief, allowing the player/viewer/etc. to immerse themselves in this fantasy realm and &amp;quot;believe&amp;quot; it for the time being. As I said in my last post, above, I'd rather deal with a sensible hardship than some utterly ridiculous and unbelievable advantage.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Message Edited by Dangon-Veeshan on &lt;span class="date_text"&gt;04-15-2006&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="time_text"&gt;06:49 PM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
